{"tid":2167233,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"高追壹傳媒的日子，第十一天，陰","createTime":"2020-08-21T03:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T02:34:28.000Z","uid":6489,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"89dc0f3049966a43840e97f441af2bbaf7d74b2a","tid":2167233,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:33:23.000Z","msg":"高追師：<br />\n到了今天，我高追剛好十一天。十一天雖然很短，但是也是我人生中最刻骨銘心的一次，我想我永遠也不會忘記，跟你在一起這十一天的日子，其實我寫這一封信給你，不是想求你爆升，因為我知道我根本沒資格要求你爆升。我只是想向你坦白，我知道坦白不能彌補我對你的傷害，但是這是我唯一可以做的事情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d947b60d5e8a4a397d95d6f91a853b47cb8c80","tid":2167233,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25269c0beec8b2204ea341f1e88426523879363a","tid":2167233,"uid":286449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:40:39.000Z","msg":"喺20大成交量老是常出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f317348bc833205636ccdd8527b5ccf0bedd3200","tid":2167233,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:41:52.000Z","msg":"啲人追埋8473架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b9505302ddaf340db4a03485e93df4c0f34752","tid":2167233,"uid":69899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09f58a5e249b1900a97728de4ae860ec07e79b9","tid":2167233,"uid":6489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:43:41.000Z","msg":"我決定左為高追壹傳媒寫日記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望可以集結成書岀版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73968077fee001a8998b56f20